author: Philippine Statistics Authority
maintainer: Philippine Statistics Authority, Office of the National Statistician
name: gross-value-added
notes: This dataset contains the Gross Value Added (GVA) in Agriculture, Fishery, Hunting and Forestry.

resources.description: This dataset contains the Gross Value Added (GVA) in Agriculture, Fishery and Forestry by Region (1985=100). This time-series includes data covering the period from 1990 to 2008 only.
resources.name: Gross Value Added in Agriculture, Fishery and Forestry by Region 1990-2008

resources.description: This dataset contains the Gross Value Added (GVA) in Agriculture, Hunting, Forestry and Fishery by Region (2000=100). This time-series includes the most recent data, covering the period from 2009 to the latest available data.
resources.name: Gross Value Added in Agriculture, Hunting, Forestry and Fishery by Region 2009-2013

resources.description: This dataset contains the Gross Value Added (GVA) in Agriculture, Hunting, Forestry and Fishing (2000 base year). This time-series includes the most recent data, covering the period from 2008 to the latest available year.
resources.name: Gross Value Added in Agriculture, Hunting, Forestry and Fishing 2008-2014

resources.description: This dataset contains the Gross Value Added (GVA) in Agriculture, Fishery and Forestry (1985=100). This time-series includes data covering the period from 1967 to 2010 only.
resources.name: Gross Value Added in Agriculture, Fishery and Forestry 1967-2010

title: Gross Value Added
